/#
   A type that describes the option premium as quoted.
 #/
record FpML5.pretrade.PremiumQuote {
  # The value of the premium quote. In general this will be either a percentage or an explicit amount.
  value : decimal

  # The method by which the option premium was quoted.
  quoteBasis : string

}

value.Doc: The value of the premium quote. In general this will be either a percentage or an explicit amount.
value.Name: value

quoteBasis.Doc: The method by which the option premium was quoted.
quoteBasis.Name: quoteBasis
